            <lg type="edition">
<l>taṉṉai yuṇarttiṉum kāyum piṟarkkunī </l>
<l>rinnīra rākuti reṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Even when I try to remove her dislike, she is displeased and says, "This is the way you behave towards (other women)."</l>
